Modu da beoryeosseo neowaui sigandeul 
Na hana dulssik neo eobsi hana dulssik ijeoga Han geulja han geulja neul sseudeon pyeonjideul 
Bol saramdo eomneunde na honjaseo ireoke Ijeneun annyeong jeongmal annyeong tteonagarago 
Hamkke haetdeon gieok modu ichyeojirago 
Ijeneun annyeong jeongmal annyeong tteonagarago 
Myeot beoneul dasi bulleodo al su eomneun neo 
Ijeneun annyeong Su eobsi tteoollyeo neowaui sigandeul 
